Note: this is equivalent to \fIset_ann(Node, [Annotation | get_ann(Node)])\fR\&, but potentially more efficient\&.
.LP
\fISee also:\fR\& \fBget_ann/1\fR\&, \fBset_ann/2\fR\&\&.
.RE
