.LP
\fISee also:\fR\& \fBadd_precomments/2\fR\&, \fBcomment/2\fR\&, \fBget_postcomments/1\fR\&, \fBjoin_comments/2\fR\&, \fBset_postcomments/2\fR\&\&.
